            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/jake/level1/jakeWorkingDoneEvening-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Jake is unbuttoning the top of his uniform, looking relieved.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>We made it. Another day, another few dollars. You going out?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Maybe. It's late.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>Late is when the fun starts. Don't be an old man. Go get a drink.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I'll think about it.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>Don't think, just do it. See you around.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 0
