<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>Best sound in the world is the lock clicking on that front door.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Finally closed.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>Yeah. Good work today. We didn't burn the place down.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Always a plus.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>Exactly. Have a good night.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
