            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/jake/level1/jakeWorkingDoneEvening-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Jake is already holding his jacket, ready to bolt out the door.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>I'm out of here before Vince asks me to mop again. If he asks, you didn't see me.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>My lips are sealed.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress3">>You're the best. Catch you tomorrow.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Take care, Jake.<</dialog>>
